My bicycle runs a Teensy++ board powered by a lead-acid battery.
A number of LEDs are wired to the board and taped to parts of
the bicycle.

Position        LEDs         Teensy PIN

In front of    White         D4
Handlebars     White         D4

Front fork,    Tri:green     E0
left side      Tri:red       E1

Front fork,    Tri:green     E1
right side     Tri:red       E0

Top-back of    Red           D6
bucket         Red           D6
